A '''Lannister bannerman''' is an unnamed recurring background character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] season. He is played by an unidentified extra and debuts in &quot;[[Fire and Blood]].&quot; He is fighting for Lord [[Tywin Lannister]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]].

